tyle=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Generation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Generation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Effects\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Effects</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Strategy\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Strategy</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Variants\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Variants</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Sporkhack\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Sporkhack</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Generation\">Generation</span></h2>\n<p>There is a 9.5% chance that a randomly-generated wand will be a wand of light, making it the most commonly generated wand.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Effects\">Effects</span></h2>\n<p>When zapped or engraved with, the wand <a href=\"/wiki/Light\" title=\"Light\">lights</a> an area with radius of 5, or the whole room if on the <a href=\"/wiki/Rogue_level\" title=\"Rogue level\">Rogue level</a>.\n</p>\n<div class=\"ttyscreen\">\n<p><span class=\"nhsym clr-lightgray\">.</span><span class=\"nhsym clr-lightgray\">.</span><span class=\"nhsym clr-lightgray\">.</span><span class=\"nhsym clr-yellow\">x</span><span class=\"nhsym clr-yellow\">x</span><span class=\"nhsym clr-yellow\">x</span><span class=\"nhsym clr-yellow\">x</span><span class=\"nhsym clr-yellow\">x</span><span class=\"nhsym clr-lightgray\">.</span><span class=\"nhsym clr-lightgray\">.</span><span class=\"nhsym clr-lightgray\">.</span><br /><span class=\"nhsym clr-ligh